<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>方式；运行方式；模式：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>mode of transport</strong>
运输方式</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>flight / energy-efficient mode
飞行 / 节能模式</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Devices in stand-by mode still use power, and older devices in this mode can use even more.
处于待机模式的设备仍会耗电，而越旧的设备耗电越多。</p><footer>外研新必修② – 6</footer></div></div>